sections.bio: Soy diseñadora y me apasiona lo que hago, me gusta escuchar a mis clientes y esforzarme para que cada proyecto sea el resultado de un proceso comunicación efectiva: Brief + Necesidades del Cliente = Imagen Corporativa. Optimizar mi tiempo para lograr ser efectiva trabajando para una empresa y como independiente, llevar varios proyectos en paralelo, adiestrar personal e impartir mis conocimientos adquiridos a grupos de personas y profesionales son algunos de los retos que he logrado enfrentar con éxito en mi carrera.

sections.About:
We participate in projects where we can draw an attractive story for your brand.

Noreste is a graphic design and art direction studio, located in Barcelona, hence (o meaning) Northeast. The direction we have clear, but how we get there we decide together with you. The end product is to have created something that will last, look fantastic, and be of great use. Cardboard, screen, glossy paper, whichever; we adapt to the format and we adapt to you. You are unique and special. Lets make this evident and make the whole world know.

sections.Hello there!:
Hello, I am Carlo Bedin, a brazilian Designer living and working in Porto Alegre, RS - Brazil.

I have 7 years of design experience, developing services of branding, strategy and brand positioning to companies and peoples.
With focus on user experience and digital design, I have a broad range experience creating designs for consumer and enterprise interfaces. My abilities span multiple platforms, the web and mobile application design in both iOS and Android platforms.

I like to develop unique experiences with strong concepts, creating incredible visual solutions that meet the needs of the project and mainly the users.

I am available for freelance projects, feel free to contact me.
